FastPattern.description: 15, SystemStatus: Trap s5Ctr {HotSwap, Problem, UnitDown, UnitUp}

FastFormatter.format: A unit is hot-swapped in an operational stack
A device failure occured
A unit is removed from an operational stack
A unit is added to an operational stack
Reason: "$5"

FastPattern.matcher: ^(\d+) ([-\w.]+)(?: \d+:\d{2}:\d{2}:\d{2} ([-\w]+))? :Web authentication from IP address ([\d.]+), access mode: ([-\w]+).*
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+(?: \d+:\d{2}:\d{2}:\d{2} [-\w]+)? :Web authentication from IP address [\d.]+, access mode: [-\w]+
^\d+ [-\w.]+(?: \d+:\d{2}:\d{2}:\d{2} [-\w]+)?.* :#\d+ Session closed \(.+\), IP address: [\d.]+, access mode: [-\w]+

FastFormatter.format: Reason: "$5"

FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+(?: \d+:\d{2}:\d{2}:\d{2} [-\w]+)?.* :#\d+ Session opened.*from IP add\S*: [\d.]+, access mode: [-\w]+

FastPattern.matcher: ^(\d+) ([-\w.]+).+([-\w]*) :User allowed \((.+)\) to log in from Web from Src IP ([\d.]+).*
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+.+:User allowed \(.+\) to log in from Web from Src IP [\d.]+
^\d+ [-\w.]+ \d+:\d{2}:\d{2}:\d{2} [-\w]+ :#\d+ Session opened\([^\)]+\) from IP add: [\d.]+, access mode: [-\w]+

FastPattern.matcher: ^(\d+) ([-\w.]+) \d+:\d{2}:\d{2}:\d{2} ([-\w]+) :User disallowed \((.+)\) to log in from Web from Src IP ([\d.]+).*
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ \d+:\d{2}:\d{2}:\d{2} [-\w]+ :User disallowed \(.+\) to log in from Web from Src IP [\d.]+

FastFormatter.format: Trap: $4
Pse Port is delivering or not power to the PD

FastPattern.description: 30, ConfigurationTrafficAudit: DHCP RELEASE/DECLINE dropped on untrusted port
FastPattern.matcher: ^(\d+) ([-\w.]+) \d+:\d{2}:\d{2}:\d{2} ([-\w]+) :DHCP Snoop:\s*(DHCP (\S+) dropped on untrusted port (\S+)) \((MAC Addr\((\w+)\) [\w ]+).*
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ \d+:\d{2}:\d{2}:\d{2} [-\w]+ :DHCP Snoop:DHCP RELEASE/DECLINE dropped on untrusted port

FastPattern.description: 31, ConfigurationTrafficAudit: DHCP REQUEST/ACK/OFFER dropped on (untrusted) port
33, ConfigurationTrafficAudit: DCHP ACK dropped on untrusted port
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ \d+:\d{2}:\d{2}:\d{2} [-\w]+ :DHCP Snoop: DHCP ACK dropped on untrusted port

FastPattern.description: 36, ServiceInfo: Telnet Logging remote {secondary-address, level informational}
40, SystemStatus: stack direction is up {Downstream, Upstream}

FastFormatter.format: System configuration is saved to NVRAM
